  "informal_statement": "For all reals a and b, the product ab is at most the square of the arithmetic mean.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "((a+b)/2)^2 - ab = (a-b)^2/4 ≥ 0. nlinarith with the square hint.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem am_gm_two (a b : ℝ) : a * b ≤ ((a + b) / 2) ^ 2",
